e":"2018-08-26T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"燥到仆街wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔俾野佢食踢鳩你<br />\n不過睇住佢妹妹吓好正"},{"pid":"5e448888b46a8203a5b9bda078c6f6807599cdf3","tid":793423,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"係咪有冇狗咁有靈性？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c267f87d0cb35637600c9b7b882387c787997764","tid":793423,"uid":203063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"佢地嬲都可愛過人 會另轉臉唔理你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c82fb35af62cf53f9b49a26c7ef13af6a040d6","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c267f87d0cb35637600c9b7b882387c787997764","tid":793423,"uid":203063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"佢地嬲都可愛過人 會另轉臉唔理你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"同意！兔用屁股對著你或其他兔代表生悶氣"},{"pid":"92e10c67ecf894ee35232fbec3a11bec648fb61c","tid":793423,"uid":36990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:36:56.000Z","msg":"性慾好強成日un"},{"pid":"bdaf83efcd824348013f9b10efe4894f8c9fcf31","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"Haha"},{"pid":"f8e0eeca8975d7772a921fa630713bcd22b2ecc4","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"兔子入樽，打籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yM0rhQxMYI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1yM0rhQxMYI&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0f6d4c13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yM0rhQxMYI</a>"},{"pid":"d67291080d9f78de2782390baf9e64804a87f830","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔兔用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下視頻可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0fb2356d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a><br />\n<br />\n兔兔很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們有poopy butthole, 可以給牠們一個butt bath, 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 關於洗澡危險 和怎樣給牠們butt bath:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=02e05c36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a>"},{"pid":"9781eee60837762a2e9ea09232a09aa92360ae5f","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。因此，兔子不喜歡被抱來抱去。當牠逃跑的時候，你還去追住抱，會令兔子和主人的信任更差。但如果主人與兔子的關係親密，牠都會喜歡同主人擁抱。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyL0yEs-ka8&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=547f483b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n最好的方法去叫牠入籠是每晚(比如：22:00）搖零食樽或pellet 樽幾下，再引牠進入籠吃。幾天後，兔子就會記得零食樽的聲音知道是時候回到籠吃。習慣後，牠會自動22:00左右提主人你是時候回到籠裡吃東西。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 有教：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRJcvi7o4YXA&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=34723dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA</a>"},{"pid":"6b673813ef6dc88a99a9be3d3406563517fc1046","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"🌟兔兔打籃球打到累了, 然後睡了😆😊🐰<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rQcoSxQj95s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrQcoSxQj95s&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=171c3f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rQcoSxQj95s</a>"},{"pid":"53476120aa4de70beb785d80c3136b427b96219b","tid":793423,"uid":39316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:26:08.000Z","msg":"原來幫兔仔沖涼佢會咁大打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學到野，樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8752e22db7538c8e37ee2eda0198449441f620b","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af89337b213aa5698aa6e73d6f867191b5b13ad3","tid":793423,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"兔洞穴究竟有幾深？🐰🌟<br />\n<br />\n原來洞穴內還可以分隔「房間」給每隻兔子😱😊<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/62vSzCsR1Zs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F62vSzCsR1Zs&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=403250be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/62vSzCsR1Zs</a>"},{"pid":"dc969343a6f8c6daed552